Spring Batch

It is a framework used to automatically process highvolume of data without the need of user interaction

It can handle efficient, transactional scheduled background task.

It is widely used in enterprise applications for tasks such as data migration, report generation, and data integration.

how does it do it:
Rather than reading, processing and writing one data at a time. It goes for handling data in chunks. That results in lower transaction overhead.

ETL (Extract-Transform-Load) process: read from source, process data, and write to destination.


popular task achieved by spring batch-

Data Migration
Report Generation
